_:N4a70e6f965734069befb3c3d36547955 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Oliver Harry is the Director for Defence and Security Exports (<abbr title=\"UK Defence and Security Exports\">UKDSE</abbr>) for the Department for Business and Trade.</p>\n\n<p>Oliver joined the UK Government around 15 years ago and has undertaken a variety of roles in London and overseas, most recently as Deputy Director in <abbr title=\"UK Defence and Security Exports\">UKDSE</abbr>.</p>\n\n<p>Before this, Oliver completed two operational deployments (including a tour as policy advisor to a Brigade Commander in Helmand province, Afghanistan) and has served as private secretary to the UK’s Minister for Defence Procurement. He has also been seconded to <abbr title=\"North Atlantic Treaty Organisation\">NATO</abbr> where he was a Deputy Director in the <abbr title=\"North Atlantic Treaty Organisation\">NATO</abbr> Secretary General’s cabinet.</p>\n\n<p>Before joining the civil service Oliver worked in the private sector. He is a fellow of the Institute of Chartered Accountants in England and Wales.</p>\n\n" .
